c: 18
v: 22
t: Bayothi babebathathu owenise wabo kwakuyinja yabo futhi (abanye) bayothi bebeyisihlanu owesithupha wabo kwakwiyinja yabo–kungukuqagela ngokungabonwayo futhi (abanye) bathi babeyisikhombisa owesishiyagalombili wabo kwakuyinja yabo ithi iNkosi yami yazi kabanzi ngesibalo sabo akekho obaziyo ngaphandle kwabambalwa ngakho-ke ungabi nempikiswano ngabo ngaphandle kwempikiswano enobufakazi obucacile futhi ungabuzi ngisho noyedwa wabo ngabo